2:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d265abbde83d7877d815a4521345e01d988c5c","tid":453139,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:14:12.000Z","msg":"快d封殺香港"},{"pid":"6201fab1be2804886aa1b1c796d2935b89817ec0","tid":453139,"uid":52276,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>竟然係01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n反了反了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n權力鬥爭想拉人落馬，政治清算黎啫，唔係以為01係清泉呀嘛？"}]}